@Node "INT" "Introduction"

@{b}@{u}Introduction@{uu}@{ub}

Use WBJoyTest to test the correct operation of the joystick connected in port
#1 or #2. Moreover, you can attach two sound samples to each directional
switch. This way, you can play up to 8 samples simply by moving the joystick
(for example to simulate a little drum kit).


@Endnode
@Node "SYR" "System requirements"

@{b}@{u}System requirements@{uu}@{ub}

WBJoyTest requires Kickstart 2.04+ and the diskfont.library in the LIBS:
directory.


@Endnode
@Node "INS" "Installation"

@{b}@{u}Installation@{uu}@{ub}

To install WBJoyTest, simply drag its icon to any drawer of your choice. If
you want to use the samples included in this archive, drag the 'Samples' icon
to the same drawer.


@Endnode
